{
  "stem": "12868.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One day, they took us to-- to-- in the factory sometimes to-- to care of heavy things, something like this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bunkers, you know, for the German airplanes, to build, or to carry cement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or like the took elderly people, they couldn't carry two bags at one time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When they couldn't, they fall down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they shoot him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 4 o'clock in the morning, 4:00. 5 o'clock sometimes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They make the appel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know appel?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is everybody got to get up, or to stay without the hats.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It can be snow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It can be rain, can be freezing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You've got to stay and to wait.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They've got to count.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans are coming, and they're counting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How many people?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How many short?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they take-- and they take us later to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And later, when you're coming back, counting again-- how many short?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On the-- on the when they carry us to the work, he got the report.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How many dead?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Back, you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "How many alive are you bringing back?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And how many dead was there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You've got to make, you know, a report, how-- to tell the SS how many-- on the places that we worked-- how many people died already, you know, were killed.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like I told you, somebody-- an elderly man, he couldn't carry three bags cement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went down on the floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He shoot him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they laid him there like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they got the report by the gate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, the appel, you know, you're staying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you wait until you get the piece of bread, till you get the-- the-- bowl of soup or something that that's what they give them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the nighttime, when we come back from the work.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
